Package: releaser
Title: Help with preparing a new version of an R package
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tanguy", "Barthelemy", , "tanguy.barthelemy@insee.fr", role = c("aut", "cre", "art"))
Description: Helps to prepare a release. Before releasing an R package it is important to update the DESCRIPTION file and the CHANGELOG. This package prepares these files and also tunes the versions according to the branches. It relies heavily on the ‘desc’ packages.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports: 
    gh, 
    desc, 
    base64enc
